{"tid":290790,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"張藝興LAY香港拍攝 女粉絲撞翻生果攤 張主動上前撿拾","createTime":"2017-06-20T05:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T11:50:21.000Z","uid":3066,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6422e4b394fe75641ce5787bfa171573957f2d9e","tid":290790,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:03:41.000Z","msg":"據台灣媒體報道，張藝興19日為《極限挑戰》到香港拍外景，所到之處吸引大批粉絲跟隨。節目錄像中，前來圍觀的女孩不小心撞到水果攤，一大盒櫻桃散落在地，他錄到一半趕緊中斷，蹲下身去幫忙撿水果，被大贊男友力爆發，網友大贊「人怎麼那麼好！」<br />\n<br />\n照片中，張藝興和一名戴帽子、穿條紋衣的女孩，再加上港星苑瓊丹[微博]等4人蹲在地上忙著撿櫻桃，大手一抓收得迅速，工作人員過來幫忙時，水果都已經撿乾淨了。他撿完櫻桃後，在回頭拿起錄像用的道具，繼續配合節目拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/130339_0817d9c2b9473d83a614ba27d5dd3b5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F130339_0817d9c2b9473d83a614ba27d5dd3b5b.jpg&h=1fe8d853&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fc5c07333eef70b63e4838bb6575fd6c23d3adf","tid":290790,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:04:24.000Z","msg":"仲要得既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216871bd73f9d75cc554f41d5dfd4c017e12e578","tid":290790,"uid":75445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:07:04.000Z","msg":"嘩 大新聞"},{"pid":"cf8a9a9101a4f21b1d92b130595e0707d31f147c","tid":290790,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:08:58.000Z","msg":"馬英九睇錶"},{"pid":"cec314510a88cb5ecf001a9cd3a74efbc5381355","tid":290790,"uid":48631,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:24:15.000Z","msg":"好人好姐叫lay,驚死人唔知佢係大陸lay🤣"},{"pid":"a064114aeccf9b959b27dba9f9dbf62df16ee337","tid":290790,"uid":61279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T08:46:07.000Z","msg":"大陸 lay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c71314400707